==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Planking
<hw>Plank"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The act of laying
planks; also, planks, collectively; a series of planks in place, as the
wooden covering of the frame of a vessel.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The act of splicing slivers. See <er>Plank</er>,
<pos>v. t.</pos>, 4.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Plank-sheer</ent>⟦br⟧
